 OpenCV Haar Cascade for Upper Body:

/usr/share/opencv4/haarcascades/haarcascade_upperbody.xml

If it's not there, you can manually download it:

wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/opencv/opencv/master/data/haarcascades/haarcascade_upperbody.xml

